line_1: Desp'rate and mad, at length He sets
The thriving pimp, who beauty sets,
line_2: Hath oft' enhane'd a nation's debts;

line_1: He minds her not; but up the Boy he sets
line_2: Upon her Back, and on the Crupper gets.

line_1: To watch, while for the Barn she sets,
line_2: She gies the Herd a pickle nits,
